data.title: Margaret Troy and James McNulty - Marriage Records
data.meta_description: Ancestry.ca has at least 1 marriage record for Margaret Troy and James McNulty, among more than 95 marriage records for the surname Troy and more than 364 marriage records for the surname McNulty.
data.text:
Ancestry.ca, the largest online family history resource, can help you explore marriage records for Margaret Troy and James McNulty from among its billions of historical records from Canada and around the world.

Marriage records are primary resources for the marriage details, since they were created at the time of the marriage. Ancestry.ca collections include indexes that can help you request the record, and in some cases, actual images of the marriage records.
